last_episode_to_air.name: Death Goes On (2)
last_episode_to_air.overview: In part two of the season finale, Jenny and Peggy are forced to face one another in a crazed scramble for life. A case involving a known gangster makes Donovan reconsider his future.

name: Coroner
overview: Jenny Cooper investigates unexplained or sudden deaths in the city of Toronto. Fierce and quick-witted, Jenny is a newly-widowed single mother with secrets of her own to unearth.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: In the aftermath of a devastating apartment fire, Jenny Cooper struggles to control a dangerous new outlet for her anxiety. Meanwhile, a witness to the fire draws Detective Donovan McAvoy into a hidden side of the city. Jenny must trust her instincts, as her father’s dementia worsens, her son turns 18, and her now-live-in boyfriend Liam is confronted by his own push and pull with death.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Coroner Jenny Cooper is moving past her trauma and embracing her whole self. In the process of healing, she and live-in boyfriend Liam are now separated.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: Emerging from a difficult loss Jenny Cooper buries herself in the city’s dead, mostly to avoid facing the trauma of her past. Det. Donovan McAvoy is determined to prove he’s fit to be back on the job.

episodes.name: Black Dog
episodes.overview: Jenny's first case as a coroner affects her personally, as she is called to investigate the death of a teen in a youth detention centre. Her own life is upended by the untimely death of her husband and she learns to navigate raising a teenage son on her own.

episodes.name: Bunny
episodes.overview: When Jenny is called to a luxe condo to investigate the death of a cannabis mogul, Vic Stenton, she enters an alternate world where nothing is as it seems. Jenny also starts to figure out what it means to live life as a widow – the good and bad.

episodes.name: Scattered (1)
episodes.overview: Jenny investigates a dismembered body that is found in Crother's Woods. Ross struggles with his dad's death.

episodes.name: Quick or Dead (2)
episodes.overview: Jenny is on the chase to stop a killer as he leaves a bloody trail of rampage across the city. The stakes are even higher when she realizes her son has been in contact with him.

episodes.name: All's Well
episodes.overview: Jenny hosts Thanksgiving at home with her dad and mother-in-law. But when the plumbing breaks down, her work life and personal life collide in the worst possible way.

episodes.name: Confetti Heart
episodes.overview: Jenny conducts her first inquest into a police shooting as Detective McAvoy confronts the brotherhood of blue.

episodes.name: The Suburbs
episodes.overview: The coroner's building is on lockdown and Jenny is isolated from her team with a blast from the past. Detective McAvoy is on the hunt for a newly released killer.

episodes.name: Bridges
episodes.overview: After the untimely death of a coworker, Jenny and Detective McAvoy dig up clues that lead back to a serial killer.

episodes.name: Fire
episodes.overview: As Jenny investigates a devastating fire in a low-income apartment building, she connects with a woman who has lost everything.

episodes.name: Borders
episodes.overview: Jenny investigates a body found in the middle of a country road with no ID, and few clues to how he got there.

episodes.name: CRISPR SISTR
episodes.overview: Jenny and Donovan investigate the death of a lab assistant, but Jenny's personal interest in the lab risks clouding the case for her.

episodes.name: Unburied
episodes.overview: Jenny investigates two grisly deaths in the suburbs, complicated by an unreliable witness.

episodes.name: One Drum
episodes.overview: In the aftermath of a mass shooting, Jenny's investigation is derailed when her exhaustion leads to dangerous consequences.

episodes.name: The Flipside
episodes.overview: Jenny assists Donovan on a case that brings them into the world of true crime podcasts. Their challenge: how do you solve a murder with no body?

episodes.name: Monster in the House (1)
episodes.overview: Jenny must trust her instincts as she takes on a new enemy that threatens to undermine her career, her family, and her own judgment.

episodes.name: Fire (2)
episodes.overview: Jenny and Donovan must race to confirm their suspicions before a dangerous suspect gets away.

Meanwhile, a witness to the fire draws Detective Donovan McAvoy into a hidden side of the city. Jenny must trust her instincts, as her father’s dementia worsens, her son turns 18, and her now-live-in boyfriend Liam is confronted by his own push and pull with death.

episodes.name: Bobby
episodes.overview: In the wake of COVID-19, Jenny investigates the mysterious death of a care worker whose body is found in her own car.

episodes.name: In Bloom
episodes.overview: When a body is found in the maze of a retreat center, Jenny uncovers uncomfortable truths about the effects of therapy.

episodes.name: Spirits
episodes.overview: Jenny and Donovan investigate a mysterious death in a "haunted house".

episodes.name: Eyes Up
episodes.overview: Jenny and Donovan help a young girl who seeks the truth about her father's death.

episodes.name: Back to the Future
episodes.overview: After a gruesome discovery at a body farm, Jenny and Donovan unearth a small town's tragic secrets.

episodes.name: No Justice, No Peace
episodes.overview: After a night of partying, Ross finds himself embroiled in a murder investigation.

episodes.name: Round and Round
episodes.overview: Clark and Jenny are forced to work together revolving around narcotics and therapy when they  catch a case involving deceased John Doe.

episodes.name: Blue Flock
episodes.overview: Jenny and Donovan confront personal dilemmas while they investigate a body on ice.

episodes.name: Christmas Eve (1)
episodes.overview: A double homicide on Christmas Eve has Jenny and Donovan uncovering the troubling secrets of a picture-perfect family.

episodes.name: Christmas Day (2)
episodes.overview: Jenny and Donovan are lured to a dangerous, remote location in search of the suspect in the Browning murders.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: Coroner Jenny Cooper is moving past her trauma and embracing her whole self. In the process of healing, she and live-in boyfriend Liam are now separated.

episodes.name: Emerge
episodes.overview: Struggling with the loss of Liam, Jenny tries to take a vacation from death and happens across a mysterious dead body that stirs suspicion in a small town.

episodes.name: Cutting Corners
episodes.overview: Jenny clashes with her replacement coroner as they navigate the decedents of a fatal car crash.

episodes.name: Neighbourhood Watch
episodes.overview: The death of an elderly Chinese restaurant owner sparks outrage in a rapidly gentrifying Chinatown.

episodes.name: Heartbeet
episodes.overview: Sparks fly as Jenny reunites with an old flame in the takedown of a large corporation. Donovan unexpectedly faces a blast from his past while trying to bring justice to a single mother.

episodes.name: Degargoony
episodes.overview: A death in a tight-knit community reveals the holes in a flawed refugee system. Gordon and Peggy's plans for a romantic weekend go awry when Jenny falls ill and must oversee a remote autopsy.

episodes.name: Young Legend
episodes.overview: In the world of basketball and cryptocurrency, Donovan and Malik find themselves at the mercy of a gifted teenager in the death of a rising basketball star.

episodes.name: True Crime (1)
episodes.overview: Jenny pieces together a distinct body clue and realizes she has seen it before. Donovan distances himself from Jenny and Malik as he leans into a support group with his ex.

episodes.name: LJND (2)
episodes.overview: Suspicious deaths lead to uncomfortable truths as Jenny, Donovan and Malik come face to face with a monster in their midst.

episodes.name: Our Home on Native Land
episodes.overview: Jenny and Donovan investigate a death in Tkaronto's unhouse community, shedding light on a major housing problem.

episodes.name: Safe Space
episodes.overview: Death follows River and Dennis as they move into a new loft. A bereaved Peggy is missing.

episodes.name: Blast to the Past (1)
episodes.overview: In part one of the season finale, Jenny and Donovan set out to find out where Peggy is and who is responsible for the explosion at Peggy’s shop.

episodes.name: Death Goes On (2)
episodes.overview: In part two of the season finale, Jenny and Peggy are forced to face one another in a crazed scramble for life. A case involving a known gangster makes Donovan reconsider his future.
